commit.message:
Add common HDL language extensions

Add support for detecting files of the common hardware description
languages of verilog and VHDL.

Suffix references, see the filename extension field of:
* Verilog: https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Verilog&oldid=964006711
* SystemVerilog: https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=SystemVerilog&oldid=962682338
* VHDL: https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=VHDL&oldid=959179032

See also:
* Xilinx UG895: Vivado User Guide, System Level Design Entry, Page 13
  https://www.xilinx.com/support/documentation/sw_manuals/xilinx2018_3/ug895-vivado-system-level-design-entry.pdf
